<section>
    <h2>Photogrammetry (3)</h2>
    <ul>
        <li class="fragment">Correct distortions, and you have a remote mapping tool (heights, distances, areas);</li>
        <li class="fragment">Removes ground survey as a map making method;</li>
        <li class="fragment">some ground survey still necessary, but only of very small areas</li>
        <li class="fragment">All topographic maps are produced using this technology.</li>
     </ul>
</section>
